Sure, here are some examples:

1. Ne želim da izgubim ovu utakmicu. (*izgubim*) (I don't want to lose this game.)
2. On je izgubio svoj novčanik na ulici. (*izgubio*) (He lost his wallet on the street.)
3. Ako nastaviš da se tako ponašaš, izgubićeš sve prijatelje. (*izgubićeš*) (If you keep behaving like that, you'll lose all your friends.)
4. Nisam izgubila nadu da će se situacija popraviti. (*izgubila*) (I haven't lost hope that the situation will improve.)
5. Iako nije bila najbolja učenica, nije želela da izgubi priliku za školovanje. (*izgubi*) (Although she wasn't the best student, she didn't want to lose the opportunity for education.)
6. U poslednjem trenutku smo izgubili avionsku kartu za let. (*izgubili*) (We lost the airplane ticket for the flight at the last minute.)
7. Ako izgubiš ovaj meč, nećeš se plasirati u finale. (*izgubiš*) (If you lose this match, you won't qualify for the final.)
8. Njihova firma je izgubila veliki posao zbog lošeg rada. (*izgubila*) (Their company lost a big job because of poor performance.)
9. Ne želim da izgubim vreme na nešto što nije važno. (*izgubim*) (I don't want to waste time on something that's not important.)
10. Iako je izgubio bitku, nije izgubio hrabrost. (*izgubio*) (Although he lost the battle, he didn't lose his courage.)

I hope these examples help!